RawLine: EXTRA_02015_Tip,趙妽從大相國寺求得的上上籤，據說此籤難求，能夠求得是天大的福氣，帶在身上有萬利而無一害。   特殊功能：內勁上升<color=#00DB00>50</color>。,赵妽从大相国寺求得的上上签，据说此签难求，能够求得是天大的福气，带在身上有万利而无一害。   特殊功能：内劲上升<color=#00DB00>50</color>。

Items.mt: The top tag obtained by Zhao Qi from the Great Sangoku Temple. It is said that this tag is hard to find, and it is a great blessing to obtain it, and there is no harm in carrying it.   Special function: Inner strength increases by 50.
